# **Part 2**

## **Describe someone living in your area who often helps others.**

One person who immediately comes to mind is an elderly woman living in my neighbourhood. Most people around here call her “Grandma Li.” Although she’s already in her sixties, she’s still extremely energetic and always willing to help people around her. I’ve known her for many years because she has lived in the same community as my family since I was a child.

What really makes her stand out is that she helps others in very practical and consistent ways rather than doing something just occasionally. For example, she often helps elderly people who live alone by buying groceries or accompanying them to hospitals. During winter, especially in northern China where the weather can be freezing, she sometimes helps clear snow near the apartment buildings to make it safer for residents to walk outside. She also volunteers in community activities and occasionally helps take care of children when their parents are busy at work.

I think her help is very beneficial because it creates a stronger sense of community. Nowadays, many people are busy with work and spend most of their time online, so neighbours sometimes barely know each other. However, people like her make the neighbourhood feel warmer and more connected. Her actions also encourage younger people to become more considerate and willing to help others.

As for why she often helps people, I think it’s mainly because she genuinely enjoys being useful and making others feel supported. From what I’ve observed, she seems to believe that helping others is not only beneficial to society, but also meaningful for her own life. Personally, I really admire her because even though she’s not wealthy or famous, she positively influences many people through small but meaningful actions.

---

## **中文翻译：**

我首先想到的是住在我家附近的一位老奶奶，大家一般都叫她“李奶奶”。虽然她已经六十多岁了，但依然非常有活力，而且总是愿意帮助别人。我小时候开始就认识她，因为她一直和我们住在同一个小区。

她特别的一点是，她帮助别人并不是偶尔做做样子，而是长期、实际地帮助大家。比如，她经常帮独居老人买菜、陪他们去医院。在中国北方冬天特别冷的时候，她有时还会帮忙清理楼下的积雪，让居民走路更安全。她还会参加社区志愿活动，有时候也会帮忙照顾一些父母忙于工作的孩子。

我觉得她的帮助非常有意义，因为她让社区更有人情味。现在很多人忙于工作，平时也总是在网上，所以邻居之间关系变得比较疏远。但像她这样的人会让社区变得更温暖、更有联系。她的行为也会影响年轻人，让大家更愿意帮助别人。

至于她为什么经常帮助别人，我觉得是因为她真的享受帮助他人的感觉。从我观察来看，她认为帮助别人不仅对社会有好处，也会让自己的人生更有意义。我非常敬佩她，因为虽然她并不富有也不出名，但她通过一些小而真实的行为积极影响了很多人。

